Class TwoDimRaggedArrayUtility

java.lang.Object
TwoDimRaggedArrayUtility
public class TwoDimRaggedArrayUtility extends Object
Manipulates a two-dimensional ragged array of doubles. This utility class will be used to create a Sales Report for Retail District. It will accommodate positive and negative numbers.
